              <div>
                <h4 class="text-purple-300 font-bold mb-1 text-sm">Choosing a Metric</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-purple-200/70">
                  <strong>Cosine</strong> is ideal for text embeddings (OpenAI, sentence-transformers) where direction matters more than magnitude. <strong>Euclidean</strong> works well for image embeddings or when magnitude is meaningful. <strong>Dot product</strong> is fastest but requires pre-normalized vectors.
                </p>
              </div>
